<section class="experience" id="experience">
	<div class="experience-content">
		<div class="experience-header">
			<h2 class="heading"><span>Experience</span></h2>
			<p class="experience-description">
				My professional journey includes hands-on experience in web development and design, 
				where I've collaborated with teams and clients to deliver impactful digital solutions. 
				From internships to freelance projects, each opportunity has shaped my approach to 
				problem-solving and strengthened my expertise in building user-centered apps.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="experience-container">
			<div class="experience-box">
				<h3>Web Development Internship</h3>
				<p>Assisted in developing web applications and gained hands-on experience in software development. Worked with modern frameworks and collaborated with senior developers.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="experience-box">
				<h3>Accenture Academy Salesforce</h3>
				<p>Created websites for small businesses and individuals, enhancing my skills in web design and development. Managed client relationships and delivered projects on time.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.experience {
		background: #F5F0E8;
		padding: 3rem 0;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
		border: 20px solid transparent;
		border-image: repeating-linear-gradient(
			45deg,
			#2C3E50 0px,
			#2C3E50 15px,
			#C0392B 15px,
			#C0392B 30px,
			#F5F0E8 30px,
			#F5F0E8 45px
		) 20;
	}

	.experience::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		background-image: 
			url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 100 100' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noiseFilter'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.8' numOctaves='4' result='noise' seed='2' /%3E%3CfeColorMatrix in='noise' type='saturate' values='0'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100' height='100' fill='%23000000' filter='url(%23noiseFilter)' opacity='0.15'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
		background-size: 100px 100px;
		pointer-events: none;
		z-index: 0;
		mix-blend-mode: overlay;
	}

	.experience-content {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		gap: 3rem;
		margin-left: 96px;
		padding: 0 2rem 0 0;
		position: relative;
	}

	.experience-content::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: 40%;
		top: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		width: 2px;
		background: linear-gradient(
			to bottom,
			transparent 0%,
			#4A1215 10%,
			#4A1215 90%,
			transparent 100%
		);
		opacity: 0.3;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
	}

	.experience-header {
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0 3rem 0 0;
		text-align: left;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		flex-shrink: 0;
		width: 40%;
	}

	.experience .heading {
		color: #4A1215;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 1px;
		font-style: italic;
		text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
		text-align: left;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.experience .heading span {
		-webkit-text-fill-color: #4A1215;
		color: #4A1215;
	}

	.experience-container {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 2rem;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		flex: 1;
		width: 60%;
		padding-left: 3rem;
	}

	.experience-box {
		background: #FFFEF8;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 0;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		border: 2px solid #4A1215;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: flex-start;
		justify-content: center;
		position: relative;
		max-width: 200px;
		aspect-ratio: 1/1;
	}

	.experience-box:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(74, 18, 21, 0.2);
	}

	.experience-box h3 {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: #4A1215;
		margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	.experience-box p {
		color: #4A1215;
		line-height: 1.5;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif;
		text-align: justify;
	}

	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.experience-content {
			flex-direction: column;
		}

		.experience-content::after {
			display: none;
		}

		.experience-header {
			width: 100%;
			margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
			padding: 0;
		}

		.experience-container {
			width: 100%;
			padding-left: 0;
		}
	}

	.experience .heading {
		color: #4A1215;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 1px;
		font-style: italic;
		text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
	}

	.experience .heading span {
		-webkit-text-fill-color: #4A1215;
		color: #4A1215;
	}

	.experience-description {
		color: #4A1215;
		font-size: 20px;
		line-height: 1.6;
		font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
		opacity: 0.85;
		margin-bottom: calc(20px * 1.6 * 5);
		position: relative;
	}

	.experience-description::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		bottom: calc(-20px * 1.6 * 5);
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: calc(20px * 1.6 * 4);
		background: 
			linear-gradient(to right, #4A1215 0%, #4A1215 100%) 0 calc(20px * 1.1) / 100% 1px no-repeat,
			linear-gradient(to right, #4A1215 0%, #4A1215 100%) 0 calc(20px * 1.1 + 20px * 1.6) / 100% 1px no-repeat,
			linear-gradient(to right, #4A1215 0%, #4A1215 100%) 0 calc(20px * 1.1 + 20px * 1.6 * 2) / 100% 1px no-repeat,
			linear-gradient(to right, #4A1215 0%, #4A1215 100%) 0 calc(20px * 1.1 + 20px * 1.6 * 3) / 100% 1px no-repeat;
		opacity: 0.3;
	}
</style>
